<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！”悟空看着扇子喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这扇子没用！铁扇公主骗了我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火势越来越大，他们只能向后退。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们该怎么办？”唐僧问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们没办法翻过山。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒举起了双手。“我们还是回家吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们写封信给佛祖，解释一下情况。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒，我们不能那么做！”唐僧责备说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，悟空说：“我曾经和铁扇公主的丈夫牛魔王是朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我有办法了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主正在她的洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她听到了敲门声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是吧。”她自言自语道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那猴子又回来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她悄悄地走到了门边向外偷看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她看到是牛魔王的时候，她高兴地打开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你回来太好了。 ”铁扇公主说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空来过了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他曾经是我的朋友。”牛魔王微笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要是能再见到他就好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的妻子有些疑惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在说什么啊？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你告诉过我，你很讨厌他的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，是吗？”牛魔王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他很粗鲁。”铁扇公主说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他让我把扇子借给他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没给他吧？”牛魔王问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然没有。”铁扇公主说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我给了他一把假扇子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那扇子看上去和真的一模一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛魔王开始踱步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空很聪明，也很厉害。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他一定会知道你骗了他，然后回来找你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们怎么办？”铁扇公主问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把扇子给我。”牛魔王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来保管扇子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主打开了一个箱子，拿出扇子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把扇子递给了她的丈夫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一道光闪过，悟空站在了她的面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我骗了你！”悟空大笑着跑出了洞穴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主气得直跺脚。“啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她丈夫回家的时候，铁扇公主还在生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“亲爱的。”牛魔王笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他的笑容马上消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出什么事情了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的朋友孙悟空来过了。”铁扇公主厉声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不是我的朋友！”牛魔王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在他打败红孩儿之前，我也从没喜欢过他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，你现在会更讨厌他的。”铁扇公主说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他偷了我的扇子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛魔王看上去很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那把扇子法力很强。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那猴子怎么偷走的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他变成了你。”铁扇公主说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“骗了我，拿走了扇子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛魔王生气了。“他怎么敢变成我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他深深地吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心。我去找那猴子，拿回你的扇子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛魔王气冲冲地走出了洞穴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空扛着芭蕉扇走在路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为成功地骗了铁扇公主，他一直高兴地笑个不停。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，他看到八戒正向他走来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒！”悟空叫了一声，“你在这里干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来帮你啊。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢，我不需要帮忙。”悟空举起了扇子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我骗了铁扇公主，拿到了真扇子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”八戒说，“我可以帮你拿着扇子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢！”悟空说着把扇子递给了八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拍了拍八戒的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们回去找师父吧。我们得......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一道光闪过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一秒钟后，牛魔王站在了悟空面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛魔王大笑道：“我骗了你，悟空！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又一道光闪过。牛魔王不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>